Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的圣诞前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃等待一直没来的她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要独自回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来之前根本没有预想到的寂寞心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在体会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天在学校碰到她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该露出什么表情好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是被人放飞机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 送我一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要去拿圣诞蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年我跟妈妈都会搞一个圣诞晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话来我们家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正蛋糕两个人又吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有剩下的话可以给你吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先送我到蛋糕店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去不去在那时候再决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反应很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原来是薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别突然咬别人的耳朵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 干脆连这边也咬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你别真的来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你叫我咬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都不会真的咬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 我跟你这么熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我疏远你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们在这里说再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 时间过得真快
