Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:50.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,600)\fad(150,150)}恶友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们初中开始认识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是三年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对 是三年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过冲击性邂逅的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有经过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 大将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在夫妇吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚钉也真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 梅原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是自愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将之称为坚强的小钉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原同学的话应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我打工的地方成为了话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过最近新建成的海港塔楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚钉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我出了个难题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人怎能去那种约会地点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那里有水族馆和天文馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是指我们三个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽然想约会的时候再去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但效果都一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为预习去一下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方 太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里都是情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了反而显得另类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看看的话怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有的是一家人去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原同学你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回到自己的座位上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学也有作为班长的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底站在哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内 内 内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（男主因紧张把内裤<パンツ>说成拳头<パンチ>）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手不错嘛 躲过了我的右勾拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤被
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在保健室里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后撞到了头跟肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是薰把我带到这里来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我打倒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 穿帮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 稍微手下留情一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经马上停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是打到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能说是停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你一直陪着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摆出那样的表情叫我怎样生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能看都薰的……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那就是我想说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没有机会让你担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 确实是很少机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时候我们经常像这样来保健室翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是那时候还是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不是来翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拘泥于琐碎的事上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰还真是一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学以来一直做些乱来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被取了玉米头核弹头的小名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用那名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了说一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后到校舍后面的花坛来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是……怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要专门叫我放学后到人烟稀少的校舍后面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰要向我告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的话就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玉米头核弹头真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不用到校舍后面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她只是中学以来的恶友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她刚才那么担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃饭 还是先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能安静点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有人睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是保健室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道江户时代因十分精确地制作日本地图的井野应高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:43.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样制作地图的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我发呆不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一的脸好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有发烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其实今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部有活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我可能忘了到这里来干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再摔倒了 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在比起梨穗子还是先担心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那条校道往左转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左转的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我对你……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么田中同学会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在好好听着惠子说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说出你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说你被选作校内男子代表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要跟他道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这种笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是笨蛋也……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说我是校内男子代表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中同学也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个怎么一唱一和了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子 快进入正题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 我向班里一位男生表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是谈这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你就好好听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个人跟我说过一短时间就会给我答复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我等了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了一段时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 等了一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子真耐心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不会等那么久的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好不容易终于把他叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜那家伙跟惠子说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说要接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚弄人也有个限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直把她放在一边不予答复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还谈什么接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后田中同学怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再一次要求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是问你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你谈些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说全校男子代表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就快点说出你的意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我的预测
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子只是被玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用那么直接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的预测怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你就说说你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写封信怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更直接的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有直接的方法的话不问我意见也能解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是写信应该写哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写我会好好等你答复之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白过一次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一直纠缠还是间接一点好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接跟他说的话他又要求接吻的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我马上试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才田中说的对象是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是不会跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中同学 能顺利发展就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下会取得前所未有的成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你说的成功总会走向坏的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我今天要做兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在那间车站前的店里做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里正举行冬季新品试食会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季新品试食会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在蟹壳里加上各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇来摇去又滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难搬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自北方的螃蟹杂锦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金针菇和风意粉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是劣拙无聊的命名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是微妙地无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要来自北方的螃蟹杂锦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的要重复说多难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要不要找其他兼职呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了餐厅招待 你还有想做的兼职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像游乐园表演节目的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是竞争率好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话会录取的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 做兼职有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱赚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一半是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看我家不是只有一位母亲和一个女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟妈妈约好了两个人一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢不在真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 她有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也今天要吃什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝冻饮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么冷的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是美也的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哥哥没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正在家里总是碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 美也要吃三文鱼和香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是以赚钱为目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过工作过程中真的很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人跟你说谢谢的时候真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来做一下也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围裙装的制服很许很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要穿围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先作为客人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心情来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你特别服务……才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天被你叫去花坛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想你会向我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错也要有个谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉挨了你一拳就变得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但薰也有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不赶快去兼职的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说搞错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着打人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不   那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天也要好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 我马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过不给你服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你决定 要便宜一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要最便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以吧 还可以自由添一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再贵一点的话就困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点就点牛排之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点冬季新品怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个来自北方的螃蟹杂锦如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个很难拿的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你看哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不是用下流的眼光看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦再倒一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我 难道我对那家伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上打他也是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学也有作为班长的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他说话维护绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想薰会向我表白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一这样说 我的心就跳得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了 您要的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着再捉弄她一次就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑嘻嘻的在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是被干劲十足做兼职的女生的迷人身姿吸引眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说不自觉看到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男生这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:24:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 接下来是看大腿看得入迷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个孩子的大腿如此有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐？

